name: The Original Bracelet
description:
This is the first bracelet We made, it uses aprox. 12 feet of Paracord.
This Bracelet will be the middle size of our bracelets. As with all of our bracelets we would like to have you send us an email with your wrist size so that we can custom make your order to perfection.

name: The In And Out Bracelet
description: This bracelet is narrower than the rest, and uses almost a foot more rope than the original. As with all of our bracelets we would like to have you E-mail us your wrist size so that we can make your order specialy.

name: Belt
description: This belt is really amazing! So cool looking that once you get it you'll want to show it off to your friends! It uses about 1 foot of rope per 1 inch of the belt. As with the bracelets we would like to have you e-mail us your waist size so that we can custom make your order.  Right now we have it on a great introductory price so order while you can!

name: How things work
description:
This is NOT a product, it's just telling you how our website works.
You can email us at paracordbraids@me.com and give us the measurements on your waist or wrist, then we can be able to make your product to fit you. Please allow 2 weeks to custom make your product, and a little more for shipping.
